sentence:
Smucker Company ( SJM ) gained nearly 7% after fiscal second quarter 2016 earnings of $1.62 per share exceeded the Zacks Consensus Estimate of $1.52 per share by 6.6% and increased 6% from the prior year
• Kirkland's Inc. ( KIRK ) shares plummeted 33% after posting second-quarter loss of $0.13 per share, wider than the Zacks Consensus Estimate of a loss of $0.06
• Shares of salesforce.com, inc. ( CRM ) gained 4.3% after posting fiscal third quarter revenue figures of $1.712 billion late Wednesday, surpassing the Zacks Consensus Estimate of $1.701 billion
• Keurig Green Mountain, Inc.'s ( GMCR ) shares jumped 18.2% after fourth-quarter fiscal 2015 earnings of 85 cents per share beat the Zacks Consensus Estimate of 70 cents by 21.4%
